 the native state. The theory outlined here shows, in\naccord with experiments, that in the steady state the native state does not\nform with unit probability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2013 13:24:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-24"}
